channel.title: Never Too Late drum sheet music
channel.description:
Ok so I was looking for a good drum tab to this song and found none so I figured I would just make some sheet music myself.
[IMG]http://i562.photobucket.com/albums/ss67/killernoob3/Nevertoolate.jpg[/img]
This is only like 1 min of the song, I'll update later when I have more.
Feel free to tell me which parts I got wrong because I know it needs work.
